<grammar><section><title>Countable and uncountable nouns</title><sectiontitle>A countable noun can be singular or plural. We can count countable nouns.  We use &lt;I&gt;a&lt;/I&gt; or &lt;I&gt;an&lt;/I&gt; for the singular.</sectiontitle><titlesound>interm_Gram_5_3_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>%undefined</text1><sound1>interm_Gram_5_3_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>I bought &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;a bicycle&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text1a><text2>%undefined</text2><sound2>interm_Gram_5_3_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>There were &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;six bicycles&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; outside her house.</text2a><sectiontitle2>Uncountable nouns usually have no singular or plural. We can't count them. We can't use &lt;I&gt;a&lt;/I&gt; or &lt;I&gt;an&lt;/I&gt;.</sectiontitle2><titlesound2>interm_Gram_5_3_4.mp3</titlesound2><text3>%undefined</text3><sound3>interm_Gram_5_3_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>He gave me &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;some information&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text3a><text4>%undefined</text4><sound4>interm_Gram_5_3_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>She has beautiful &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;hair&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text4a></section><section><title>Countable and uncountable nouns</title><sectiontitle>With uncountable nouns we often use &lt;I&gt;a ... of&lt;/I&gt; to show the number.</sectiontitle><titlesound>interm_Gram_5_3_7.mp3</titlesound><text1>%undefined</text1><sound1>interm_Gram_5_3_8.mp3</sound1><text1a>I found &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;a lot of money&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text1a><text2>%undefined</text2><sound2>interm_Gram_5_3_9.mp3</sound2><text2a>They gave me &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;a piece of paper&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text2a><sectiontitle2>Countable and uncountable nouns use &lt;I&gt;some, not any&lt;/I&gt;, and &lt;I&gt;a lot of&lt;/I&gt;. Countable nouns use &lt;I&gt;many&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;a few&lt;/I&gt;.  Uncountable nouns use &lt;I&gt;much&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;a little&lt;/I&gt;.</sectiontitle2><titlesound2>interm_Gram_5_3_10.mp3</titlesound2><text3>There weren't &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;many cars&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text3><sound3>interm_Gram_5_3_11.mp3</sound3><text3a>There wasn't &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;much traffic&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text3a><text4>They played &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;a few songs&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text4><sound4>interm_Gram_5_3_12.mp3</sound4><text4a>They played &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#3300cc'&gt;a little music&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text4a></section></grammar>